Gunslik is the owner of Gunslik's Assorted Items, a general store found in the wealthy half of Keldagrim. Gunslik's shop stocks a variety of wares, ranging from basic supplies such as empty pots to slightly more difficult-to-obtain items such as charcoal and rope.
